{"hash":"gridsome","data":{"label":{"id":"tag: vue","name":"vue","type":"tag","belongsTo":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"68","title":"用 Vue 做 PWA（一）：开始","path":"/post/vue-pwa-1/","summary":"\n<p>Vue 党快速上手 PWA</p>\n","createdAt":"2020-01-30T07:59:20.000Z","lastEditedAt":"2020-07-21T00:47:51.000Z","image":null,"labels":[{"id":"blog: programing"},{"id":"series: vue-pwa"},{"id":"tag: vue"}]}},{"node":{"id":"80","title":"Vue 加 Hammer 处理手势","path":"/post/vue-hammer/","summary":"\n<p>接近原生 App 体验，手势是少不了的。但是无论是 Vue 还是 Vuetify 对手势的支持并不好，于是需要 <code>Hammer.js</code> 支持。</p>\n","createdAt":"2020-01-27T08:33:10.000Z","lastEditedAt":"2020-07-03T02:20:23.000Z","image":null,"labels":[{"id":"blog: programing"},{"id":"tag: vue"}]}},{"node":{"id":"87","title":"用 Vue 做 PWA（二）：Runtime Caching","path":"/post/vue-pwa-2/","summary":"\n<p>本系列已经很久没更新了，在此讨论实践过程中遇到的 Runtime Caching 的一些问题。主要注意点是在处理跨域请求上。</p>\n","createdAt":"2020-04-18T04:49:20.000Z","lastEditedAt":"2020-07-10T08:34:16.000Z","image":null,"labels":[{"id":"blog: programing"},{"id":"series: vue-pwa"},{"id":"tag: vue"}]}},{"node":{"id":"96","title":"Writing Blog with GitHub Issue and Vue Apollo","path":"/post/vue-iblog/","summary":"\n<p>Some tricks when using vue-apollo to communicate with GitHub API v4</p>\n","createdAt":"2020-04-24T00:00:00.000Z","lastEditedAt":"2020-06-21T12:56:05.000Z","image":"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/8247e9229615919a1a751e67dbac8d50b6558046/68747470733a2f2f61706f6c6c6f2e7675656a732e6f72672f6c6f676f2e706e67","labels":[{"id":"blog: programing"},{"id":"tag: vue"}]}},{"node":{"id":"147","title":"用 Vue 做 PWA （三）：理解生命周期","path":"/post/vue-pwa-3/","summary":"\n<p>虽然前两节的内容足以写出能用的 service worker，但是如果深入细节，仍然会有一些“匪夷所思”的现象发生。</p>\n","createdAt":"2020-09-03T02:40:57.000Z","lastEditedAt":"2020-09-03T04:11:23.000Z","image":null,"labels":[{"id":"blog: programing"},{"id":"series: vue-pwa"},{"id":"tag: vue"}]}}]}}},"context":{}}